/*--------------------------------------------------------*/
/* BSW/bios2bswif.h                                       */
/*--------------------------------------------------------*/
CREATED:NO

bios2bswif.h
|- *u1g_bios2bswif_acelthl  accel throttle opening 0-100[%]
|- *u1g_bios2bswif_brkpdl   brake pedal opening    0-100[%]
|- *u1g_bios2bswif_clthpdl  clutch pedal opening   0-100[%]
|- *u1g_bios2bswif_gear     gear status    1,2,3,4,5,6,N[-]
|- *u1g_bios2bswif_igsw     ignition status 0(off),1(on)[-]

rename and publish the swift label.

/*--------------------------------------------------------*/
/* BSW/bschedulif.h                                       */
/*--------------------------------------------------------*/
CREATED:NO

bschedulif.h
|- *u1g_bscheduleif_cnt     called count[-]
|- *u1g_bscheduleif_rstflg  reset flag[-]
|- ^vdg_bscheduleif_call()

Each time it's called from swift, the internal count is 
incremented by one count.
1 count -> call 4msmng 4 times.
2 count -> call 16msmng 1 times.
4 count -> call 64msmng 1 times.

